                <strong style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 5px;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="8 17 12 21 16 17"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"></line><path d="M20.39 18.39A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.3"></path></svg> Response Payload:</strong>
